OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start for most
OL,6,Fbut warm bright or sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping and also scattered
OL,8,Fafternoon showers, these locally heavy
OL,9,Fwith a low chance of thunder. Winds
OL,10,Fremaining generally light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny evening showers fading to
OL,13,Fvariable cloud and some clear spells,
OL,14,Fwith isolated mist or fog patches
OL,15,Fpossibly forming in places. Winds
OL,16,Fremaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
