OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FBright or sunny spells but
OL,6,Fturning cloudier through the evening
OL,7,Fas scattered showers move south, with
OL,8,Fa cooler northerly breeze arriving
OL,9,Fovernight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and mostly dry,
OL,13,Falthough isolated, mainly light
OL,14,Fshowers still possible. Cooler
OL,15,Fmidweek, with patchy overnight rural
OL,16,Fgrass frost possible, turning milder
OL,17,Fagain later. Winds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
